title: Config colors
description: You can set the color of the screen in the config menu

title: Select preset.
description:
Select some of the preset colors.
They are based on the most common CRT screens, VGA, Green Phosphor, white monochome etc.
Adjust the brightness and contrast with the sliders.

title: Barrel
description: Also you can djust the barrel of the screen.

title: CRT barreling.
description:
Activate the barrel effect with the checkbox control.
Adjust it with the sliders.
There are three presets, wide, tall and square. You can modify the browser window to adjust them.

title: Export
description: You can export your page settings as a json file.

title: Import
description: You can also import the saved json into another Presentron page, like Videomator
